body_html:
We took TensorBoard out of the TensorFlow repo and into http://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard.

So it's expected that attempting to build or depend on TensorBoard source from the TF repo won't work.

Ah, but if the pip command is broken, I should look into that.

body:
We took TensorBoard out of the TensorFlow repo and into http://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard.

So it's expected that attempting to build or depend on TensorBoard source from the TF repo won't work.

Ah, but if the pip command is broken, I should look into that.
